We're kicking off our first est film production with a momentous Malvern Home renovation by @dohertydesignstudio from est magazine issue #35.
.
Tapping into its rich architectural past and 1980s new wave bones, @dohertydesignstudio have skilfully commandeered an epic journey to reinvent this Melbourne family home. An original 1980's design by architect Peter McIntyre. .
.
Experience the entire home via the link in profile or read the full feature in est magazine issue #35. .
.

.
View all three films via link in profile.
.

Creative Direction | Design @robmillsarchitects

THE NEW FACES OF EST LIVING EDITORIAL | Karen McCartney
​.

RESIDENTIAL DESIGN | AIDA Awards
​.
​Congratulations to @flackstudio_ for taking out the @auinteriordesignawards Residential Design award for their Potts Point House – a joint winner with @architectseat for their Bellows House in Flinders, Victoria. 
​.
A series of reveals throughout an 1930's home, @flackstudio_ principal and founder David Flack was tasked with ensuring the four-storey terrace in Potts Point, Sydney had continuity with the history of the city while guaranteeing practical, contemporary living for its owners. 
​.
​Read more about Potts Point in our feature on estliving.com – link in profile. 
​.
​Design @flackstudio_
